quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  28,29,"“Mûsa pamene adakwaniritsa nyengoyo, adanyamuka ndi banja lake (kubwerera kwao) adaona moto kumbali ya phiri. Adauza banja lake: “Dikirani ndithudi ine ndaona moto mwina mwake ndingakutengereni nkhani za kumeneko kapena chikuni cha moto kuti muothe.”"
  28,30,"“Tsono pamene adaudzera, adaitanidwa kuchokera mbali ya kumanja ya chigwacho, pa malo wodalitsidwa kuchokera mu mtengo, ankati: “E iwe Mûsa! Ndithudi Ine ndi Allah Mbuye wa zolengedwa.”"
  28,31,"““Ndipo ponya (pansi) ndodo yakoyo.” Choncho pamene adayiona ikugwedezeka monga kuti iyo ndi njoka, adatembenuka kuthawa ndipo sadachewuke. (Adauzidwa): “E iwe Mûsa! Bwera kuno, usaope. Ndithu iwe ndiwe mmodzi wokhala ndi mtendere.”"
  28,32,"“Lowetsa dzanja lako m’thumba mwako (palisani la mkanjo wako), lituluka lili loyera, popanda choipa. Ukachita mantha, fumbata dzanja lako chakukhwapa; (ukatero mantha akuchokera). Izi zidzakhala zizindikiro ziwiri zochokera kwa Mbuye wako kwa Farawo ndi nduna zake. Ndithu iwo ndianthu olakwa.”"
  28,33,"“(Mûsa) adanena (moopa) “E Mbuye wanga! Ine ndidapha munthu mwa iwo, ndipo ndikuopa kuti akandipha.”"
  28,34,"““Ndipo m’bale wanga (Haaruni) ndikatswiri pakuyankhula kuposa ine. Mutumizeni pamodzi ndi ine monga mnthandizi, azikandivomereza (pa zimene ndizikanena). Ndithu ine ndikuopa kuti akanditsutsa.”"
  28,35,"“(Allah) adati: “Tilimbitsa dzanja lako ndi m’bale wakoyo ndipo tikupatsani kupambana, iwo sangafikitse masautso pa inu; chifukwa cha zozizwitsa zathuzo inu awiri ndi amene akutsatireni, ndinu opambana.”"